{"tid":631248,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"中國古拳 蝗馬拳 恐失傳","createTime":"2018-04-16T09:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T10:54:42.000Z","uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bba616a80bee26ab4f1362f01fb63b8ee4a9592a","tid":631248,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T09:57:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180415/640_aff156812d9e1f742cdd6c242cefdf1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180415%2F640_aff156812d9e1f742cdd6c242cefdf1f.jpg&h=39a4cf2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n狗拳！又名地龍拳！乃是一種發跡中國南方、以地面戰為主的精妙拳法，日前已被列入中國國家級非物質遺產文化名錄，無奈現代的年輕人一聽到「狗拳」兩字，馬上就直搖頭說不想學，掌門人黎偉軍也十分憂心，這套流傳百年的古拳法恐怕就要失傳！<br />\n根據《梨視頻》報導，佛山市武術協會副主席黎偉軍是中國目前少數精通狗拳的大師，他在接受訪問時坦承收不太到弟子、擔心政府若不再好好保護，狗拳恐怕就要消失，但網友看完他示範之後卻滿頭問號，「確定真的只是名字不好聽嗎......？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180415/1335104/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180415%2F1335104%2F&d=0955fzHkKFo8gU5cknr%2BF9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=a25cc45c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180415%2F1335104%2F&h=4768b02d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180415/1335104/</a>"},{"pid":"39a465434d6072644a1e7fe12e00aad661a73bc6","tid":631248,"uid":12034,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:18:11.000Z","msg":"王騎射尿?"},{"pid":"c0f1bde185eb01f95952b1697607503d7b4cbceb","tid":631248,"uid":76488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:19:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca0041623847336646976c7aaf3120914ae8c800","tid":631248,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:21:38.000Z","msg":"嗰幾下後撐腳做乜鳩"},{"pid":"a49876ae073272d5abc9506d4ea07b5773a988f1","tid":631248,"uid":181651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"